RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT B.TICKET_ID FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, TLTB_CONTRACT_MASTER B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.LATEST_VERSION_NO = B.VERSION_NO AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS = 'A' AND A.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND A.MODULE_CODE = 'TL' AND A.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'T' AND NVL(B.INTERNAL_TRADE,'N') <> 'Y' AND NVL(B.TRADE_IDENTIFIER,'**') <> 'SC' AND B.TRADE_DATE <= ? AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM TLTBS_SETTLEMENT_MASTER WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND SETTLE_STATUS = 'Y') AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM TLTBS_CONSOL_TICKET_MASTER O,TLTBS_CONSOL_TICKET_DETAIL P WHERE O.CONSOL_TICKET_REF_NO = P.CONSOL_TICKET_REF_NO AND P.TICKET_ID = B.TICKET_ID AND O.CONSOL_TICKET_AUTH_STATUS <> 'A') AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM TLTBS_CONSOL_TRADE_DETAIL WHERE TICKET_ID = B.TICKET_ID AND SETTLEMENT_REQD = 'Y' AND TRADE_SETTL_STATUS IN ('U','M','F','E','W')) AND A.BRANCH = Global.Current_Branch
SELECT b.customer_no,b.customer_name1 FROM oltms_customer b WHERE b.auth_stat = 'A' AND b.record_stat = 'O'

SELECT b.counterparty, b.ticket_id,b.currency, b.contract_ref_no FROM oltbs_contract a, tltbs_contract_master b WHERE a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no AND a.latest_version_no = b.version_no AND a.contract_status = 'A' AND a.auth_status = 'A' AND a.module_code = 'TL' AND a.product_type = 'T' AND NVL(b.internal_trade, 'N') <> 'Y' AND NVL(b.trade_identifier, '**') <> 'SC' AND b.trade_date <= ? and b.agency_id IS NOT NULL
SELECT ccy_code,ccy_name FROM cytms_ccy_defn WHERE ccy_code NOT IN (SELECT currency FROM tltbs_consol_ticket_assign_fee WHERE consol_ticket_ref_no=? AND counterparty=?)

select b.trade_ref_no,a.ticket_id,a.agency_id from tltbs_consol_ticket_detail a,tltbs_consol_trade_detail b,oltbs_contract c WHERE a.consol_ticket_ref_no = ? AND a.consol_ticket_ref_no = b.consol_ticket_ref_no AND a.ticket_id = b.ticket_id AND b.trade_ref_no = c.contract_ref_no AND c.counterparty = ? AND b.settlement_reqd = 'Y' AND c.contract_status = 'A' AND c.auth_status = 'A' AND a.agency_id IS NOT NULL AND b.trade_ref_no NOT IN (SELECT trade_ref_no FROM tltbs_consol_ticket_assign_fee WHERE consol_ticket_ref_no = ?) and not exists(select 1 from tltbs_contract_fee_master p where p.contract_ref_no = b.trade_ref_no and tlpks_fee_services.fn_get_fee_type(sypks_utils.get_product(B.TRADE_REF_NO),p.component) = 'AS' AND event_seq_no = (select max(event_seq_no) FROM tltbs_contract_fee_master v where v.contract_ref_no = b.trade_ref_no and V.component = p.component) AND p.waiver = 'Y')
SELECT CCY_CODE,CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN order by ccy_code

SELECT SSI_MNEMONIC,SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO FROM OLTM_INSTR A,OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.BRANCH ='ALL' AND A.MODULE='AL' AND A.COUNTERPARTY= ? AND A.CURRENCY = '*.*' AND A.PRODUCT_CODE ='ALL' AND A.AUTH_STAT ='A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND B.CUSTOMER_NO=A.COUNTERPARTY ORDER BY SSI_MNEMONIC

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_SUMMARY_WHERECLAUSE: exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = PRODUCT_CODE AND USER_ID = global.user_id)
